Problem Statement
Artisans often struggle to reach a wider audience and sell their handmade products due to limited access to e-commerce platforms that cater specifically to their needs. Many existing marketplaces prioritize mass-produced goods, making it difficult for small-scale creators to compete. Additionally, artisans face challenges in managing inventory, shipping, and marketing their work without the necessary tools and support.

This project aims to create a dedicated e-commerce platform where artisans can easily showcase, sell, and manage their unique handcrafted products, while buyers can discover and purchase these one-of-a-kind items directly from the creators. The platform will provide a seamless, supportive environment for artisans to grow their businesses and connect with a global audience that values craftsmanship.
